                <h2>We making moving houses easier and stress free!</h2>
                <p>
                    When people change their location they are required to update their address details with all their organisations and government agencies. A single person can have affiliations with hundreds of organisations. Manually updating these details can become cumbersome and stressful during a time that can already be stressful. Time is not only wasted, but some government agencies require prompt updates, with legal ramifications for failing to do so. There is also the possibility of people not receiving important mail.
                </p>
                <p>
                    There is currently no efficient way to address this problem. Identity Right, aims to address this problem by creating a central system that allows <b>you</b> to store these details. You will have the freedom to always update your details using one easy interface. With your permission organisations will be able to access this data to ensure that they always have up to date information about you.
                </p>

                <h2>Advantages of having your address managed by us.</h2>
                <p>
                    <ul style="text-align:justify;list-style: url;">
                        <li>
                            Reduces stress during moving houses.
                        </li>
                        <li>
