                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Instant update to all organisations your profile is linked to.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            No more lost mail.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Have the flexibility to provide certain details to particular organisations.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Avoid paying nasty fines because you forgot to change your address with a government organisation.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

            </div>
        </div>
    }
